PN,38301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FAurigny has confirmed two planes will
OL,7,Fserve Alderney from Easter Weekend,
OL,8,Fjust two days after hundreds protested
OL,9,Fat the island's airport.
OL,11,FJust one Twin Otter aircraft has
OL,12,Fserved Alderney, operated by Isles of
OL,13,FScilly airline Skybus, since Aurigny's
OL,14,FDornier plane was retired on 13
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FFrom Easter, a second, newly rebuilt
OL,18,FTwin Otter will be stationed in
OL,19,FGuernsey - this will also be run by
OL,20,FSkybus.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FBoth Twin Otters will wear Skybus
OL,7,Fbranding until the beginning of June,
OL,8,Fafter which time one of the planes
OL,9,Fwill be run by Aurigny and display its
OL,10,Flivery.
OL,12,FFrom October, a third, Skybus-run MSN
OL,13,F664 - a sister aircraft to the Twin
OL,14,FOtter - will be based in Guernsey as a
OL,15,Fbackup.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FAurigny says staff training for the
OL,7,Froute has been delayed by poor weather
OL,8,Fconditions and aircraft availability
OL,9,Ffollowing Storm Goretti, but insists
OL,10,Fthis will be complete by the end of
OL,11,FJune.
OL,13,FUntil then, journeys will be completed
OL,14,Fby selected staff who are still
OL,15,Fcompleting their training and will be
OL,16,Fsupported by qualified Skybus crews.
OL,18,FJeannie Cameron, Alderney's Chair of
OL,19,Fthe Policy and Finance Committee,
OL,20,Fpreviously said the island had "lost
OL,21,Fconfidence" in Aurigny.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FHowever, she has now tentatively
OL,7,Fwelcomed the news of a second plane
OL,8,Fserving the island, believing it will
OL,9,Fmake "a huge difference" to islanders.
OL,11,F"The proof is in the pudding," Jeannie
OL,12,Ftold ITV News. "We want to see the
OL,13,Fdelivery, and then we will be able to
OL,14,Fconfirm that things are back on track.
OL,16,F"And until such time, we will be
OL,17,Fkeeping a very close watch on what's
OL,18,Fgoing on."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FMore than 200 residents were at
OL,7,FAlderney Airport on Sunday 22 March to
OL,8,Fcriticise Aurigny's handling of the
OL,9,Fisland's routes, after the airline
OL,10,Fannounced disruptions to flights
OL,11,Fserving lifeline routes to Guernsey
OL,12,Fand Southampton.
OL,14,FAurigny is blaming staff sickness and
OL,15,Fa crew shortage at Skybus.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FSkyBus Managing Director, Jonathan
OL,7,FHinkles, has "apologised unreservedly"
OL,8,Fto the community, adding that his
OL,9,Fcompany is "falling short of what is
OL,10,Fexpected" and will "build appropriate
OL,11,Fresilience".
OL,13,FOne of the protestors, Nigel Dupont,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We can't go on like this. The
OL,15,Fisland is suffering everywhere, from
OL,16,Fbusiness to tourism."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FAurigny has defended its record,
OL,7,Fexplaining that in January and
OL,8,FFebruary this year, just 1.7% of its
OL,9,Fflights were cancelled due to
OL,10,Ftechnical or personnel issues.
OL,12,FIn addition, out of more than 1,000
OL,13,Fflights which have taken off since the
OL,14,Fbeginning of 2026, 88% have been on
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,FAurigny also insists that its new Twin
OL,7,FOtter planes offer better performance
OL,8,Fin wet weather than the retired
OL,9,FDornier, as well as equal crosswind
OL,10,Fresistance and night-time flight
OL,11,Fcapability.
OL,13,FKevin George, Chairman at Aurigny,
OL,14,Fstated: "Both the Board and Management
OL,15,Fat Aurigny take the concerns raised by
OL,16,Fthe local population and political
OL,17,Frepresentatives in Alderney extremely
OL,18,Fseriously.
OL,26,@vD@IOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774458667
OL,3,CSecond plane to serve Alderney from
OL,4,CEaster
OL,6,F"While our controllable performance
OL,7,Fhas clearly been better since the
OL,8,Fintroduction of the Twin Otter
OL,9,Fcompared to the same period last year,
OL,10,Fwe are determined that future
OL,11,Fperformance will build further on
OL,12,Fthese foundations.
OL,14,F"Our aim is for all stakeholders to
OL,15,Fshare our confidence in the future,
OL,16,Fand that is why we are taking
OL,17,Fimmediate measures together with
OL,18,FSkybus to strengthen operational
OL,19,Frobustness and ensure operational
OL,20,Fperformance to the highest standards
OL,21,Fwell into the future."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
